METRIX

The game is written in smileBASIC and can run with
Petite Computer on Nintendo DS/3DS: http://www.petitcomputer.com

Use the QR codes PNG to transfer the source code into the system.

Or create new QR codes on changes with the petite editor:
http://www2.u-netsurf.ne.jp/~ozawa/petitcom/petiteditor.html


